---
import { SITE } from '../config/site';

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "Do you offer financing for spray foam or full attic upgrades?",
    answer:
      "Yes. We work with financing partners for qualified homeowners so larger envelope upgrades can move forward on a predictable monthly plan.",
  },
  {
    question: "How fast can you schedule blown-in removal or spray foam?",
    answer:
      "Most projects start with a short site visit. Removal and reinstall timing depends on attic access, scope, and drying requirements after water events.",
  },
  {
    question: "Can you help with insurance documentation after storms or leaks?",
    answer:
      "Yes. We capture photos, moisture context, and written scopes that align with what adjusters expect for insulation tear-out and replacement.",
  },
  {
    question: "What insulation systems do you install?",
    answer:
      "Spray foam (open and closed cell where appropriate), blown-in fiberglass and cellulose, radiant barriers, and hybrid attic strategies tailored to Florida humidity.",
  },
  {
    question: "Do you provide free insulation consultations?",
    answer:
      `Yes. We provide a free initial consultation and written recommendations before work begins across ${SITE.serviceAreas.slice(0, 3).join(", ")}, and nearby markets.`,
  },
  {
    question: "How long does a typical attic spray foam project take?",
    answer:
      "Many residential attic scopes finish in one to two days depending on square footage, prep, ventilation details, and whether removal is required first.",
  },
];
---

<section class="section section--alt">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-label">FAQ</span>
      <h2>Insulation questions, answered</h2>
      <p>Financing, timelines, Florida humidity, and what to expect before we seal your envelope.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-list">
      {faqs.map((faq) => (
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>{faq.question}</summary>
          <p>{faq.answer}</p>
        </details>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .faq-list {
    display: grid;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .faq-item {
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    background: var(--panel);
    padding: 0.95rem 1.1rem;
    box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .faq-item p {
    margin-top: 0.65rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 0.93rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }
</style>
